dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jacob Torres. May I have your name, please?
Hi Jacob! My name is Hannah Hayes.
Nice to meet you, Hannah! Can you please provide me with the first three digits of your policy number?
Thank you, Hannah. One more piece of information we need is the address where the incident occurred. Could you please provide that for us?
Of course, the incident took place at one two three Maple Street.
Thank you for providing that information, Hannah. We will review the details of your claim and get back to you as soon as possible.
Thank you, Jacob. I appreciate your assistance.
You're welcome, Hannah. If you have any further questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Goodbye!
